name: Cypher Neuromancer
description:
This piece is the Cypher Neuromancer. 
In Psybonacci's universe, the entity doesn't "rule it all" and there is a lot of mystery involved. The Neuromancer assigned himself for the task of keeping the gates safe from the Corruption. Inside the control room, the simulation is steady.
